Package: NextWordR
Type: Package
Title: An R-package/Shiny-application for word prediction
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Boyd", email = "mikuana@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/Mikuana/NextWordR
BugReports: https://github.com/Mikuana/NextWordR/issues
Description:
  A Shiny application embedded directly into the package that it relies on, which performs
  text prediction based upon user input and returns word suggestions based upon a dictionary which
  was built using a corpus of data provided by the SwiftKey company.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
    magrittr,
    dplyr,
    quanteda,
    htmltools,
    shiny,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: testthat
